Business Brief -- Salton/Maxim Housewares Inc.:
   Macy's Chapter 11 Filing
   Results in Charge for Period
The household and personal care appliances concern said
its net receivables outstanding from Macy as of Monday were
$927,000. Sales to Macy and its affiliates accounted for 20%
of the company's net sales in 1991, Salton/Maxim said.
   Salton/Maxim said it will continue to ship products to
Macy's stores with effective debtor-in-possession financing
in place.